            <p class="text-white">** Members of the Champion will be offered internship places at Deloitte's "Consulting Digital Team" to be held in Hong Kong SAR with a monthly internship allowance of HK$8100 each x up to 3 months (subjects to passing a selection process to be conducted by Deloitte), Cash value total HK$121,500.</p>
            <p class="text-white">*** Subjects to passing a selection process to be conducted by Xiaomi</p>
            <p class="text-white">**** Details will be provided to the female hackers upon acceptance to the hackUST2021.</p>
            <br>

            <p class="text-white">HKUST reserves the right to make the final interpretation of the above and final arrangement for the event.</p>
          </div>
        </div>    
